4| z^2 \implies 2|z \implies z = 2b
\begin{align}3^{2a} - 5^y &= (2b)^2\\ 5^y &= 3^{2a} - (2b)^2\\ 5^y &= (3^a + 2b)(3^a - 2b)\end{align}
(3^a - 2b) > 1
\begin{align} &a,b > 0, a \in \mathbb{Z}\\ \implies &3^a + 2b > 3^a - 2b \ge 1\\ \implies &3^a + 2b > 1\end{align}
